<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Scourge2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Scourge,</orth> vb. to whip, to lash: <cit><quote>I am whipped and --d with rods,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.239" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 239</bibl></cit>. <emph>with them</emph> (tresses) <cit><quote>s. the bad revolting stars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 4</bibl></cit>. == to chastise, to afflict: <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.102" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.171" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 171</bibl> (Ff <emph>plague</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ant 2.6.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 6, 22</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>